    "before_footer": "/* Platform-specific peripheral selection and validation. */\n#define MCS_PWM_TIMER_HANDLE (&htim1)\n#define MCS_PWM_ADC_TRIGGER ADC_EXTERNALTRIGINJEC_T1_TRGO"
